    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to packaging.package_type. Business justification: Semiconductor pricing contracts are package-type specific — BGA, QFN, and flip-chip carry different unit prices and NRE costs. Linking price_agreement to package_type enables package-level pricing rep' ;
